---
title: Crumbed Chicken Dippers & Rosemary Wedges with Garlic Aioli & Apple Salad
description: We’re officially making chicken (dippers) tonight, so don’t be afraid to break out your best chicken dance! We recommend spooning over the delicious garlic aioli, but these are called dippers, so if you need to grab 'em and dunk 'em, we won't tell anyone. Promise.
